text: Stephen Farrell (born 18 June 1965) is a British former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:British male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Great Britain Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stoke-on-Trent
